WEBVTT

00:00:57.560 --> 00:01:00.600
It's impossible to tell if she's really insane or not.

00:01:07.760 --> 00:01:11.240
Husband, I made these osmanthus cakes for you myself.

00:01:11.600 --> 00:01:14.440
Caiyue told me they're your favorite.

00:01:20.680 --> 00:01:22.480
How can I eat if you don't feed me?

00:01:34.600 --> 00:01:35.600
Husband,

00:01:35.640 --> 00:01:36.800
I have a question.

00:01:37.320 --> 00:01:39.360
Since we are already married,

00:01:39.479 --> 00:01:41.479
why haven't you touched me for days?

00:01:43.240 --> 00:01:44.160
Slow down.

00:02:06.320 --> 00:02:08.280
Caiyue, I need to go out for a while.

00:02:08.400 --> 00:02:09.360
I'll be back soon.

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:11.039
Yes, Madam.

00:02:38.240 --> 00:02:39.280
Sinan.

00:02:40.079 --> 00:02:41.120
Yiyu.

00:02:43.720 --> 00:02:45.000
Your face...

00:02:46.079 --> 00:02:47.000
I'm fine.

00:02:47.480 --> 00:02:48.810
How's it going with you?

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:51.240
To be honest,

00:02:51.480 --> 00:02:54.410
I don't know if he's really crazy or just pretending.

00:02:54.600 --> 00:02:56.560
I don't want to keep trying. I...

00:02:56.600 --> 00:02:57.480
Yiyu.

00:02:58.600 --> 00:03:01.330
If you give up now, all our efforts will be wasted.

00:03:03.680 --> 00:03:04.560
Yiyu

00:03:13.120 --> 00:03:15.120
Please bear with it a little longer.

00:03:38.240 --> 00:03:38.880
Madam.

00:03:38.960 --> 00:03:40.960
The young master's madness has flared up again.

00:03:40.960 --> 00:03:42.680
Since you arrived at the mansion,

00:03:42.680 --> 00:03:44.120
the young master seemed much better.

00:03:44.120 --> 00:03:45.560
But today after coming back from outside,

00:03:45.560 --> 00:03:46.760
he must have encountered something.

00:03:46.760 --> 00:03:49.040
Several sets of expensive tableware in this house

00:03:49.040 --> 00:03:50.300
have all been smashed.

00:03:50.320 --> 00:03:51.480
These past few days,

00:03:51.600 --> 00:03:54.680
I've never seen him lose his temper like this.

00:03:54.760 --> 00:03:56.620
What's suddenly gotten into him?

00:03:57.640 --> 00:03:59.720
Then bring him a few more sets of bowls to smash.

00:03:59.720 --> 00:04:00.640
Yes.

00:04:11.320 --> 00:04:12.320
Tell me.

00:04:13.840 --> 00:04:16.240
I'm going to make a cut right here.

00:04:16.680 --> 00:04:19.320
Does Sinan still have feelings for you?

00:04:20.600 --> 00:04:22.040
What are you doing?

00:04:23.040 --> 00:04:25.600
I just want to know if Sinan truly loves you

00:04:26.120 --> 00:04:27.720
or if she's just pretending.

00:04:27.840 --> 00:04:29.600
Young master, have you forgotten?

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:31.400
I am your wife now.

00:04:32.320 --> 00:04:33.400
Is that so?

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:35.760
Young master! Young master!

00:04:35.760 --> 00:04:37.120
Please calm down, young master.

00:04:37.120 --> 00:04:37.960
Young master!

00:04:47.880 --> 00:04:48.680
Fire!

00:04:50.120 --> 00:04:52.120
There's a fire!

00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:53.320
Fire! Fire!

00:04:53.400 --> 00:04:55.400
Dad! There's a fire!

00:05:25.080 --> 00:05:26.320
Sinan!

00:05:26.520 --> 00:05:28.760
I'm afraid Liu Silin has truly gone mad.

00:05:29.040 --> 00:05:30.800
I can't stay here another day.

00:05:30.880 --> 00:05:32.540
Please take me away from here.

00:05:41.400 --> 00:05:43.330
Yiyu, thank you for your hard work.

00:05:43.520 --> 00:05:45.920
I'll wait for you in the west alley at the Hour of Zi tomorrow.

00:05:45.920 --> 00:05:48.440
I'll take you to a hideout in the city for now.

00:06:04.480 --> 00:06:06.680
Madam, why are you here?

00:06:08.040 --> 00:06:11.900
I'm here to check on the medicine being prepared for the young master.

00:06:13.080 --> 00:06:14.520
I need to get rid of her

00:06:14.560 --> 00:06:15.520
so I can escape.

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:18.480
The young master's illness seems quite serious this time.

00:06:18.480 --> 00:06:20.480
The doctor has prescribed new herbs

00:06:20.880 --> 00:06:23.010
that need to be simmered for two hours.

00:06:24.960 --> 00:06:25.960
This medicine...

00:06:26.720 --> 00:06:27.680
Let me.

00:06:28.440 --> 00:06:29.320
You...

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:32.080
you can go back now. I'll deliver it myself.

00:06:32.280 --> 00:06:33.280
Yes.

00:06:46.280 --> 00:06:48.159
Madam, I'll take my leave.

00:06:55.000 --> 00:06:56.280
Run! Hurry!

00:06:56.880 --> 00:06:57.880
Over here!

00:06:58.120 --> 00:06:59.040
Darling.

00:06:59.440 --> 00:07:00.880
Get down. Stay down.

00:07:04.720 --> 00:07:05.840
Don't make a sound.

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:07.040
Did you hear me?

00:07:07.160 --> 00:07:08.440
Don't let them escape.

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:11.160
You heard that, right?

00:07:11.160 --> 00:07:11.840
Hurry.

00:07:11.880 --> 00:07:13.120
Your Highness.

00:07:56.680 --> 00:07:59.610
This jade pendant has appeared in the Liu residence.

00:08:13.880 --> 00:08:15.340
Yiyu, get in the carriage.

00:08:18.560 --> 00:08:21.880
Sinan, I can't go with you this time.

00:09:10.560 --> 00:09:12.720
Young master, why aren't you in bed yet?

00:09:12.720 --> 00:09:14.280
It's so late.

00:09:15.000 --> 00:09:16.130
Where have you been?

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:18.360
I can't sleep.

00:09:18.440 --> 00:09:20.000
Just went out for a walk.

00:09:43.440 --> 00:09:44.560
Madam.

00:09:47.640 --> 00:09:48.800
It's about to snow.

00:09:49.080 --> 00:09:50.340
Please go back inside.

00:09:51.760 --> 00:09:54.240
I'll check on the potted plants in the yard.

00:09:54.440 --> 00:09:55.700
Don't let them freeze.

00:09:56.520 --> 00:09:57.360
Don't worry.

00:09:57.440 --> 00:10:00.040
I had someone bring them in early this morning.

00:10:04.240 --> 00:10:04.920
Caiyue.

00:10:05.640 --> 00:10:07.880
I noticed your jade pendant yesterday. It's exquisite.

00:10:07.880 --> 00:10:09.560
May I have a look at it?

00:10:11.200 --> 00:10:12.000
Sure.

00:10:24.800 --> 00:10:26.800
This is it. No mistake.

00:10:30.880 --> 00:10:35.240
Caiyue, this jade pendant is of fine craftsmanship.

00:10:35.320 --> 00:10:36.560
The quality is exceptional.

00:10:36.560 --> 00:10:38.000
Where did you get it?

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:40.440
To be honest with you, Madam,

00:10:40.440 --> 00:10:42.120
it's a family heirloom.

00:10:42.440 --> 00:10:43.680
When my mother got married,

00:10:43.680 --> 00:10:45.480
my grandmother passed it to her.

00:10:45.560 --> 00:10:47.820
After my mother died, it was passed to me.

00:10:49.560 --> 00:10:52.880
Caiyue, I really like this jade pendant.

00:10:52.920 --> 00:10:55.680
I'd like to find a craftsman to make one just like it.

00:10:55.680 --> 00:10:56.540
Would you mind?

00:10:56.800 --> 00:10:58.080
Not at all.

00:10:58.320 --> 00:10:59.440
If Madam likes it,

00:10:59.560 --> 00:11:01.080
I'm more than happy.

00:11:02.000 --> 00:11:04.200
May I borrow it for a couple of days then?

00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:05.320
Yes.

00:11:15.200 --> 00:11:18.680
Miss, your jade pendant has such a smooth and delicate texture,

00:11:18.680 --> 00:11:20.640
its color is pure white like cream,

00:11:20.800 --> 00:11:22.520
it's premium Hetian jade.

00:11:23.000 --> 00:11:27.000
And this mutton-fat jade is especially precious among Hetian jade.

00:11:27.240 --> 00:11:29.000
Only wealthy families

00:11:29.120 --> 00:11:31.800
would possess such a valuable pendant.

00:11:34.120 --> 00:11:37.120
Caiyue's family has been poor for three generations.

00:11:37.200 --> 00:11:39.730
This jade pendant couldn't possibly be hers.

00:11:46.560 --> 00:11:47.560
Are you all right?

00:11:47.760 --> 00:11:48.680
Qian Yiyu.

00:11:48.760 --> 00:11:50.760
Are you blind or do you have a death wish?

00:11:50.760 --> 00:11:52.960
How dare you block the Commander's car!

00:11:53.000 --> 00:11:54.080
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

00:11:54.080 --> 00:11:55.610
Move along now! Move along!

00:12:02.840 --> 00:12:05.080
Let's go. My father is waiting.

00:12:10.440 --> 00:12:11.360
Come, Yiyu.

00:12:11.800 --> 00:12:13.920
Oh no, madam. Please.

00:12:16.880 --> 00:12:18.800
Weren't you taken away by the second young master?

00:12:18.800 --> 00:12:21.000
How did you end up back in Yuncheng?

00:12:21.920 --> 00:12:23.440
It's a long story.

00:12:23.760 --> 00:12:26.890
I was caught and brought back by the eldest young master.

00:12:27.000 --> 00:12:29.130
What about you? Why are you still here?

00:12:30.440 --> 00:12:31.880
I never planned to leave.

00:12:32.360 --> 00:12:35.920
Aren't you afraid the Liu family will find you?

00:12:38.320 --> 00:12:40.650
I've lived in Yuncheng since I was a child.

00:12:41.120 --> 00:12:42.980
I don't know where else I could go.

00:12:44.120 --> 00:12:47.560
Besides, I still have unfinished business in Yuncheng.

00:12:52.120 --> 00:12:53.000
What about you?

00:12:53.240 --> 00:12:54.840
Will you try to escape again?

00:12:55.320 --> 00:12:56.320
No more running.

00:12:56.520 --> 00:12:59.680
I've decided to stay and find the real killer.

00:13:00.120 --> 00:13:01.080
Real killer?

00:13:01.440 --> 00:13:02.440
That's right.

00:13:02.680 --> 00:13:06.010
The person who killed my birth parents is in the Liu mansion.

00:13:26.120 --> 00:13:26.600
Yu.

00:13:30.720 --> 00:13:31.450
Long Hongxu.

00:13:31.760 --> 00:13:32.320
Guang Yandi.
Zhiguang.

00:13:32.320 --> 00:13:32.920
Yandi Bao.

00:13:35.880 --> 00:13:37.080
Shi, Di, Tao, Lei, Wen, Li, Bin.

00:13:37.080 --> 00:13:38.360
Tao, Lei, Wen, Li, Bin, Ping, Cai, Chao, Lei Pengchao, Chang, Ting, Yue.

00:13:38.360 --> 00:13:39.120
Lei Pengchao.

00:13:39.120 --> 00:13:39.720
[Credits]

